   version stable 4.3.7 4.3.6 4.3.5 4.3.4 4.3.3 4.3.2 4.3.1 4.3.0
   require expat gcc-g++ gnutls ncurses readline
      opts --disable-static
  category network/ftp
 attribute console makej
    source http://ftp.yars.free.net/pub/source/lftp/ \
           http://www.kanshima.net/mirrors/lftp/ \
           lftp-$VERSION.tar.xz
      info last 20120530
      info home http://lftp.yar.ru/
      info mail http://lftp.yar.ru/list.html
      desc 'sophisticated ftp/http client, file transfer program
Like BASH, it has job control and uses readline library for input.
It has bookmarks, built-in mirror, can transfer several files in parallel.
It was designed with reliability in mind.'
